name: ShotTarget
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: shot target
des:
Shot target is a shooting game that targets the screen. You need a device with a display to play. 
You hit closer point to the center, higher score will be given, so aim the center and say shoot center. 
Eight bullets are given per game. 
When you say reset, the total score becomes 0 points, 8 bullets are given again, and you can restart the game.

Skill Invocation: Alexa, open shot target
Shoot: shoot center, shoot the center, shot center, shot the center, hit center, hit the center
Reset: restart, reset
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
